^^^^^

-  **jpg** - ``image/jpeg``
-  **jpx** - ``image/jpx``
-  **png** - ``image/png``
-  **gif** - ``image/gif``
-  **webp** - ``image/webp``
-  **cr2** - ``image/x-canon-cr2``
